    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404770/extras/98554722117d338f3c10e0147cbdb12f.avif?t=1728309359\" width=564 height=138 /></span> <br><br>Have you ever felt trapped? Like you want to escape your leathery prison?<strong> It's time to upgrade your cock to freedom in <i>Chicken Tricks</i>!</strong> Fight through waves of enemies for your good ol' american freedom, using all the weapons at your disposals... Which aren't many, because <strong>you're a chicken</strong>... ya know. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404770/extras/597700b5931d5d84729038bbc07eeb45.poster.avif?t=1728309359\" width=564 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404770/extras/597700b5931d5d84729038bbc07eeb45.webm?t=1728309359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404770/extras/597700b5931d5d84729038bbc07eeb45.mp4?t=1728309359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Peck, poisons, explosive eggs, everything just works in <i>Chicken Tricks</i></strong>. Use them to defeat your enemies, which will grant you with a determined amount of XP. Once you have enough, you will level up, which lets you<strong> choose one of 4 possible upgrades</strong>. Choose new abilities to slap your way through making new and different builds avoiding death.<br><br>Each level, the spawn rate of mobs raises and, each 5 levels, several improved enemies will spawn, making sure of making your mission harder to accomplish. If you get killed while at maximum level possible, a little surprise awaits. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404770/extras/623be38e019781bf371faab6450c9d85.poster.avif?t=1728309359\" width=564 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404770/extras/623be38e019781bf371faab6450c9d85.webm?t=1728309359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2404770/extras/623be38e019781bf371faab6450c9d85.mp4?t=1728309359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Just do anything to make sure you don't become another one in the line of the next KFC frier, and save your legacy from that doomed fate!</strong>",
